<title>USA: Banc One plans press conference on merger.</title>
<headline>Banc One plans press conference on merger.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-01-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Banc One Corp and Monday it will hold a press conference today to discuss its merger with First USA.</p>
<p>Under the merger, announced earlier, Banc One would buy First USA in a deal valued at $7.3 billion. It would form the third-largest U.S. credit card operation with about 32 million cardholders and assets of $35 billion.</p>
<p>The press conference is scheduled for 1400 EDT at the Plaza Hotel in New York.</p>
